    <div class="clause">
      <span class="clause-num">{{#if guarantor_name}}7{{else}}6{{/if}}.{{#if has_garden}}14{{else}}13{{/if}}</span>
      <strong>Contents Insurance (Premium Requirement):</strong> The Tenant shall obtain and maintain adequate contents insurance for personal belongings and third-party liability cover of at least £1,000,000 throughout the tenancy. Proof of insurance must be provided to the Landlord within 14 days of the tenancy start date.
