      <ul class="obligations-list">
        <li>give at least 28 days' notice in writing;</li>
        <li>leave the Property clean and in the same condition as at commencement (fair wear and tear excepted);</li>
        <li>return all keys, access devices and security fobs;</li>
        <li>remove all personal belongings;</li>
        <li>provide a forwarding address.</li>
      </ul>
