    <div class="subsection-title">By the Landlord</div>
    <div class="clause">
      <span class="clause-num">{{#if guarantor_name}}9{{else}}8{{/if}}.2</span>
      The Landlord can only end the tenancy by:
      <ul class="obligations-list">
        <li>serving a Notice to Leave stating the eviction ground(s);</li>
        <li>waiting for the notice period to expire (28 or 84 days depending on the ground);</li>
        <li>applying to the Tribunal for an eviction order;</li>
        <li>obtaining an eviction order from the Tribunal;</li>
        <li>having the order enforced by sheriff officers (if necessary).</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="clause">
